https://futurism.com/ibms-watson-ai-recommends-same-treatment-as-doctors-in-99-of-cancer-cases/
AGENT
IBMâ€™s Watson & Human experts at the University of North Carolina School of Medicine 
GOAL
To contribute to the healthcare industry and medical researches specially oncology. 
DATA
Nearly 1,000 cancer diagnoses cases.
METHODS
AI to analyze 1,000 cancer diagnoses and recommend treatments accordingly.
RESULTS
Watson was able to recommend the same treatment which are the actual treatments from oncologists in 99% of the cases. Also because it can read and analyze thousands of medical documents in minutes, Watson found treatment options human doctors misplaced in 30% of the cases.
COMMENTS
It is promising that artificial intelligence is put in good use for medical purposes.

